## Troubleshooting

### Metro Won't Start

```powershell
# Check if port 8081 is in use
Get-NetTCPConnection -LocalPort 8081

# Kill process
Get-Process -Id (Get-NetTCPConnection -LocalPort 8081).OwningProcess | Stop-Process -Force

# Start fresh
npx expo start --clear
```

### Emulator Won't Open

```powershell
# List available emulators
emulator -list-avds

# Start manually
emulator -avd pixel_5_-_api_34

# Then press 'a' in Expo
```

### "Cannot find module"

```powershell
# Clear everything
Remove-Item -Recurse -Force node_modules
Remove-Item package-lock.json
npm install
npx expo start --clear
```

### Fast Refresh Not Working

1. Press 'r' to reload
2. If still broken: Ctrl+C, then `npm start`
3. Nuclear option: Clear cache (see above)

