## Version Control (Git)

### What to Commit

```
✅ .cursor/          # Rules
✅ docs/             # Documentation
✅ src/              # Entire Expo project
   ✅ src/app/       # Expo Router screens
   ✅ src/domain/    # Business logic
   ✅ src/data/      # Data layer
   ✅ src/presentation/ # UI components
   ✅ src/infrastructure/ # External services
   ✅ src/assets/    # Images, icons
   ✅ src/app.json
   ✅ src/package.json
   ✅ src/tsconfig.json
✅ .gitignore
✅ todo.md
```

### What NOT to Commit (Already in .gitignore)

```
❌ src/node_modules/
❌ src/.expo/
❌ src/android/ (only if using expo prebuild)
❌ src/ios/ (only if using expo prebuild)
❌ *.log
❌ .env
```

